---
import { Phone, ArrowRight } from "lucide-astro";
---

<section id="contact" class="py-20 md:py-28 relative overflow-hidden">
    <!-- Background - Flat blue -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-primary-600"></div>

    <!-- Subtle pattern overlay -->
    <div
        class="absolute inset-0 opacity-5"
        style="background-image: url('data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iNjAiIGhlaWdodD0iNjAiIHZpZXdCb3g9IjAgMCA2MCA2MCIgeG1sbnM9Imh0dHA6Ly93d3cudzMub3JnLzIwMDAvc3ZnIj48ZyBmaWxsPSIjZmZmIiBmaWxsLXJ1bGU9ImV2ZW5vZGQiPjxjaXJjbGUgY3g9IjMwIiBjeT0iMzAiIHI9IjIiLz48L2c+PC9zdmc+');"
    >
    </div>

    <div class="container-custom relative z-10 text-center">
        <div
            class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-white/10 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6"
        >
            <Phone class="w-8 h-8 text-white" />
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
            Besoin d'un système qui tourne sans vous ?
        </h2>

        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-white/80 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            Décrivez votre contexte. Je vous propose un plan concret pour stabiliser site, serveur, sécurité et automatisation, sans intermédiaires.
        </p>

        <a
            href="/contact/"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-3 px-8 py-4 bg-primary-50 text-primary-800 font-bold text-lg rounded-xl hover:bg-primary-100 transition-all duration-300 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1"
        >
            <ArrowRight class="w-5 h-5" />
            <span>Démarrer maintenant</span>
        </a>
    </div>
</section>
